# Market Moves 2025 (Trading Wrapped)

## Product rules (must follow before coding)
- Mobile-first layout.
- Desktop: center app in 390px fixed-width "Phone Container" with black borders.
- Dark mode only with neon accents; "vibe coded" aesthetic.
- Use Next.js App Router + Tailwind CSS + Framer Motion.
- Data is hardcoded locally (components or local data module); no external APIs.
- 5-7 animated slides, Instagram/TikTok story feel.
- Visual vibe: Tokyo/Shibuya, anime realism, neon blues/oranges.

## Core features
- Story navigation: tap left/right to navigate; progress bar at top.
- Fullscreen background media (video/image) with dark overlay.
- Animations: staggered text, counting numbers, spring physics.

## Design system
- Background: #0a0a0a; typography: Inter or Geist Sans.
- Heading weight 800, body 500.
- Profit: #00FF94, Loss: #FF3366, Neutral: #888888.
